      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL ADORE (5) progressive filly with a good record over this track and trip. Returned from a let-up with a plugging third over 1000m at this track. Fitter now and can stalk the good tempo and finish over the top of them. CHRISTMAS STAR (7) given the gun run along the inside before getting the upper hand late with a tough neck win over this course and distance. Jumps 3kg in weight today but draw a soft gate. Sure to be thereabouts. SPIRITS BURN DEEP (4) back in class and trip and will relish the fast speed. Covered ground early without cover before fading to finish ninth over 1300m at Newcastle in BM68 class. Value player who can return to form. MONTE CRUISE (6) finished second over 1000m at Nowra two back then missed the frame last time out over 1100m at Hawkesbury. Winkers come off. In the mix.",
